{"id": 2674, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些关于“真正的感情”的定义，你觉得都是瞎胡扯？", "description": "说出“真正的爱情／友情／亲情就得怎么怎么样做”......做不到就是不够格，这真的不是情感绑架吗？（题图来自：iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 3609, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181214104900elsDa87LGXvIQJzR.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318208, "content": "我还爱你，只是不喜欢你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537943}, {"id": 318210, "content": "我都是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529652}, {"id": 318211, "content": "我单身不是因为我有什么问题，而是因为没找到合适的人（来配合我）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 318212, "content": "爱就是奉献", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725839}, {"id": 318468, "content": "长久忍耐和包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511295}, {"id": 318213, "content": "父母必须对子女无条件付出，什么都要以子女优先。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720470}, {"id": 318214, "content": "爱情里的两个人不是物质的匹配，而是精神的想通。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537968}, {"id": 318215, "content": "爱情里的两个人不是物质的匹配，而是精神的相通。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537968}, {"id": 318217, "content": "一见钟情", "image": "img/option/option/20181221141532BHq93ji6p0XsTOJ7", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535882}, {"id": 321033, "content": "希望有人比我还爱你 \n又希望没人有我这么爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548993}, {"id": 318218, "content": "那真正的感情应该是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537977}, {"id": 318220, "content": "爱你是没有理由的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369252}, {"id": 318221, "content": "常把“兄弟”挂嘴边，却在做一些对兄弟不利的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537285}, {"id": 318223, "content": "喜欢一个人不需要理由", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432679}, {"id": 318991, "content": "不合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499484}, {"id": 318226, "content": "都是🐔\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500646}, {"id": 318227, "content": "真的感情，就算没有在一起，但是当自己难受时，ta会说我一直都在", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531194}, {"id": 318230, "content": "女生就是用来宠的（我是女生）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491715}, {"id": 320279, "content": "打骂都是爱？！朋友之间就是不怕互相麻烦？！呸！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935711}, {"id": 318232, "content": "分开时说 我不是一个薄情的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061598}, {"id": 318233, "content": "我写了一天总结 不到1000字 哎我体育生", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277606}, {"id": 318234, "content": "会喜欢你本来的样子的。", "image": "img/option/option/20181221153537tK97LflcYxegnCET.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530522}, {"id": 318237, "content": "我都是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498759}, {"id": 318238, "content": "我真的为你付出了很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498759}, {"id": 318239, "content": "你为什么一点都不关心我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498759}, {"id": 318240, "content": "感情哪有确切的定义，每个人选择爱的方式都不同，尊重每一次选择，尊重多元。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538041}, {"id": 318242, "content": "我喜欢你，与你无关", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 321058, "content": "等一个等不到的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549226}, {"id": 318246, "content": "我还是只相信患难才能见真情，哪怕平时联系少，但一到自己落魄的时候，能在自己身边的人才是真情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496020}, {"id": 318247, "content": "真正的感情无法被统一定义，如何诠释全看个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536787}, {"id": 316457, "content": "真正好的感情是不需要经营和维系的", "image": null, "praise_count": 498, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 318250, "content": "感情里应该毫无隐瞒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465519}, {"id": 316459, "content": "不喜欢听朋友诉苦的人不是真正的朋友／不配做好朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 204, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 318251, "content": "真正美好的感情一定是排他的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934803}, {"id": 316461, "content": "真正爱你的人就是爱你本来的样子，不需要做出改变，怎么样都不会离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 742, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 319277, "content": "我爱你？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 318259, "content": "永远爱一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413278}, {"id": 318262, "content": "有情人终成眷属", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537705}, {"id": 318518, "content": "只能是他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540227}, {"id": 318265, "content": "我能想到你最浪漫的是，就是和你一起慢慢变老😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 318266, "content": "爱一个人需要理由吗？需要吗？不需要吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516911}, {"id": 318268, "content": "人性的复杂，决定了很多事情不可能都那么简单就能被解决好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949058}, {"id": 318269, "content": "你连她的屎都不肯吃，凭什么说你爱她！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538125}, {"id": 318270, "content": "一见钟情。\n不就是看脸的高级形容？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538131}, {"id": 318271, "content": "如果她真的爱你不会在乎你有没有钱。。。穷人意淫", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 318272, "content": "做彼此的舔狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538139}, {"id": 318273, "content": "感情这种事情别人说的都是胡说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277821}, {"id": 318530, "content": "我爱你，永远", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146873}, {"id": 319044, "content": "找一个爱你的人，而不是你爱的人····\r\n总要有一方学会忍让对方·····", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 318278, "content": "真正的感情应该是自私的，失去理智的！（你可长点心吧，大家都是成年人了，干什么都要负责的！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371145}]}